<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/721488-my-friends-and-people-i-follow-are-all">My friends and people I follow are all over the place with their ratings on this book - from one star to five stars. It sounds like my sort of story. Is the writing lame?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
